{"tid":2441163,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果豬隊友亂象有感，心生一計。","createTime":"2021-03-10T12:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T13:25:49.000Z","uid":372210,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b776278b129e15327768c4a35a7372fa94982532","tid":2441163,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"見時事台屌哂鬼話抹黑蘋果又剩，不過諗深一層，又唔錯得哂嘅。<br />\n<br />\n一嚟，老實講蘋果豬隊友都唔係第一日嘅事，<br />\n二嚟，放且蘋果賣嘅嘢政府自己本身唔知咩，<br />\n三嚟，對家都會買蘋果，正如689都會攞蘋果嚟抆屎。<br />\n<br />\n宜家蘋果最大嘅問題就係成日將啲唔適當嘅嘢放頭版，而且次次都係噉，柒完一獲又一獲。<br />\n<br />\n不過諗深一層，蘋果咪又係因為冇廣告冇嘢放頭版先柒。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">既然你阻止唔到個編輯寫乜，倒不如諗下點封下佢支筆啦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">所以我建議，時事台與其喺度屌鬼，不如學下之前噉，眾籌登頭版啦。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一嚟噉樣你想寫咩都得。<br />\n二嚟可以封住個編輯把口，唔畀佢亂寫嘢。<br />\n<br />\n至少每次有預感個編輯會亂寫嘢就要即刻眾籌登頭版，最好就日日登，唔好畀機會佢亂寫嘢，以香港人眾籌嘅能力，我相信一日過百萬唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">眾籌要人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n時事台手足今日課咗未？今日課完聽日再課<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"08636af419a5ef578f9b4cb32a7fc0c5b06b0c34","tid":2441163,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭版登乜閪廣告"},{"pid":"3a70c4e001c60869c6156bf187f1886ef3ce851f","tid":2441163,"uid":372210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08636af419a5ef578f9b4cb32a7fc0c5b06b0c34","tid":2441163,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:24:08.000Z","msg":"你戇鳩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n頭版登乜閪廣告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"Brian Cha夠可以喺頭版登全版廣告啦，點解唔得？再唔係唔登廣告囉，你有錢想寫咩都得㗎。"}]}